PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Gingerbread Cookies
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What makes your gingerbread cookies special?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our gingerbread cookies are made from scratch using only the finest ingredients like real butter, brown sugar, molasses, and warm spices. Each cookie is hand-cut and baked to perfection for maximum flavor and a delightfully crisp texture.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How long do the gingerbread cookies stay fresh?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our gingerbread cookies will stay fresh for up to 2 weeks when stored in an airtight container at room temperature. For longer storage, you can freeze the cookies for up to 3 months.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Do you offer any special holiday designs?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, we offer a variety of festive gingerbread cookie designs perfect for the holidays! From classic gingerbread men to intricately decorated trees, stars, and more. Check our seasonal offerings for the latest designs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I place a custom order for a special occasion?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! We accept custom orders for any occasion. Whether you need a gingerbread house centerpiece or favor boxes, our bakers can create custom designs just for you. Simply contact us with your requirements.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Find answers to common questions about our handcrafted gingerbread cookies
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What makes your gingerbread cookies special?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our gingerbread cookies are made from scratch using only the finest ingredients like real butter, brown sugar, molasses and premium spices. Each one is hand-cut and baked to perfection for an authentic, homemade taste.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How long do the cookies stay fresh?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: When stored properly in an airtight container, our gingerbread cookies will stay fresh for up to 2 weeks. For best flavor, we recommend enjoying them within 5-7 days of receiving your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Do you offer gluten-free or vegan options?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, we have both gluten-free and vegan gingerbread cookie varieties available. These are made in a dedicated gluten-free facility with plant-based ingredients.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I customize my gingerbread cookies?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! We offer customization options like decorative icing, colorful sprinkles, and personalized messages written on the cookies. Just let us know your preferences when ordering.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We offer flat rate shipping anywhere in the continental US. Expedited 2-day and overnight shipping is also available for an additional fee. All orders are carefully packaged to ensure your gingerbread cookies arrive fresh and unbroken.
